title: Radiohead 7 Television Commercials Xvid/DivX (1998)
description:
7 Television Commercials is the only official collection of music videos currently available from Radiohead, covering the period from their The Bends (1995) to OK Computer (1997) albums with seven songs in all. The VHS home video (later reissued as a DVD, with no additional features) was released on 4 May 1998 in the United Kingdom, and on 30 June in the United States. The box art, by Stanley Donwood and Thom Yorke, is composed almost entirely of elements from the artwork for OK Computer.

Video type
34:03 Xvid. Tested on Philips DVP3140/37 DVD player.

Video list
   1. "Paranoid Android"
   2. "Street Spirit (Fade Out)"
   3. "No Surprises"
   4. "Just"
   5. "High and Dry" (U.S. version)
   6. "Karma Police"
   7. "Fake Plastic Trees"
